<div class="featureDetails"> <h2>Are you caring for aging parents or a loved one?</h2> <p>Is it a
struggle to coordinate all the activities and events? Is it a constant challenge to keep friends and
family informed? Do you wish you could enlist more help from other members of the care circle? Caregaroo
provides simple-to-use online tools to help you communicate and coordinate care for your loved ones.</p>

</div>

</div>  <!-- end  feature 1-->

