<div class="featureRight grid_6">

<img class="featureImage" src="img/feature2.jpg" alt="full deeplink support" /> </div>

<div class="featureDetails withIcon"> <h2>Share News</h2> <p>Create an online community around your
loved one by inviting friends, family and other members of the care community to join a private network
dedicated to your loved one. Exchange news and share updates on health, upcoming needs and daily
activities. With Caregaroo it is now easy to keep everyone informed and up to date.</p> </div>

</div>  <!-- end  feature 2-->


