<div class="featureDetails"> <h2>Coordinate Care</h2> <p>List activities and ask members of the care
community volunteer to get things done. Need a ride to a medical appointment or help with meal
preparation? With Caregaroo, it is easy to communicate what you need help with and organize
contributions of the community towards improving your loved one’s quality of life.</p>

</div>

</div>  <!-- end  feature 3-->


<div id="feature4" class="feature grid_14">

<div class="featureRight grid_6">


<img class="featureImage" src="img/feature4.jpg" alt="user editable playlist" />


