<div class="featureDetails"> <div class="featureDetails"><h2>Works with Email</h2> <p>Since it’s not
possible to stay logged into Caregaroo around the clock, you can choose to be notified via email when
something important happens in your network. You can also send updates and respond to messages directly
from your email. Can’t find that old email you are looking for? No problem, Caregaroo makes it easy to
find and track all communications.</p> </div>

</div>  <!-- end  feature 4-->


